    "name": "Wererat (Human Form)",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Natural wererats tend to be short and wiry, with constantly darting eyes and frequent nervous twitches. Males often have thin, ragged moustaches.<br/><br/>Wererats prefer cities where they can blend in with the humanoid and rat population. Their abilities make them especially good at thieving and spying, and in many cities the thieves\u2019 guild employs numerous wererat members."
        }
    ],
